#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the man KIO worker you are able to read the man pages installed on "
"your system. It is easy to use:"
msgstr ""
"S pomočjo KIO worker-ja za man lahko berete strani man, ki so nameščene na "
"vašem sistemu. Uporaba je lahka:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the sections of the manual, click to find the rest."
msgstr "Oglejte si razdelke priročnika, kliknite, da najdete ostalo."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>fopen</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>fopen</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the man page of <command>fopen</command>."
msgstr "Oglejte si man stran za <command>fopen</command>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>fopen(3)</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>fopen(3)</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the man page of <command>fopen</command> in section 3."
msgstr "Oglejte si man stran za <command>fopen</command> v razdelku 3."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the index of section 3."
msgstr "Oglejte si indeks sekcije 3."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>man:/</command>intro<replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:/</command>intro<replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the introduction of section 3."
msgstr "Oglejte si uvod v razdelek 3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there are more than one man page of the name that you have entered, you "
"will get a list where you can choose the man page that you want to see."
msgstr ""
"Če obstaja več kot ena man stran, ki se nanaša na vnešeno ime, boste dobili "
"seznam, kjer lahko izberete man stran, ki si jo želite ogledati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also a shortcut: <userinput><command>#fopen</command></userinput>, "
"which has the same effect as above."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja tudi bližnjica: <userinput><command>#fopen</command></userinput>, ki "
"ima enak učinek kot zgoraj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not find all your man pages, adjust the configuration file "
"<filename>/etc/manpath.config</filename> (or a file of a similar name "
"depending on your distribution) or adjust the environment variables "
"<envar>MANPATH</envar> and <envar>MANSECT</envar>."
msgstr ""
"Če ne najdete vseh strani man, prilagodite konfiguracijsko datoteko "
"<filename>/etc/manpath.config</filename> (ali datoteko s podobnim imenom, "
"odvisno od vaše distribucije) ali prilagodite okoljski spremenljivki "
"<envar>MANPATH</envar> in <envar>MANSECT</envar>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with any other KIO worker, it is possible to enter a &URL;, like "
"<userinput><command>man:/socket</command></userinput> in <emphasis>any</"
"emphasis> &kde; application. Try it in &kwrite; and you will see the man "
"page in &HTML; format."
msgstr ""
"Kot pri vsakem drugem KIO worker-ju lahko vneste &URL;, kot je "
"<userinput><command>man:socket</command></userinput> v <emphasis>katerikoli</"
"emphasis> program &kde;. Poskusite v &kwrite;-u in videli boste stran man v "
"formatu &HTML;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contact mailing list: <email>kde-devel@kde.org</email>"
msgstr "Kontaktirajte poštni seznam: <email>kde-devel@kde.org</email>"

